to activate
.\venv\Scripts\activate

within environment execute the entry file
python ./app.py

to deactivate
deactivate

used packages
flask
flask_socketio

for deployment we will need
wsgi server 

and also 
pip install gunicorn eventlet

Guicorn and WSGI (Web Server Gateway Interface) used in deploying and serving python web apps, specifically those built with web frameworks like Flask and Django

generate requirements using
pip freeze > requirements.txt